# AWS Infrastructure Source of Truth (SOT) & Disaster Recovery Framework

## Overview

This repository demonstrates an Infrastructure Source of Truth (SOT) and Disaster Recovery framework built using AWS, Terraform, and AWS CLI.

The solution provides:

* Automated AWS infrastructure inventory collection
* Daily infrastructure backup snapshots
* Infrastructure discovery and audit reporting
* Terraform-based Disaster Recovery (DR)
* Multi-account and multi-region support
* Infrastructure as Code (IaC) best practices

## Key Features

### Infrastructure Inventory

* Daily collection of AWS resources using AWS APIs
* Automated backup generation and archival
* Region-wise infrastructure snapshots
* Audit and compliance reporting

### Disaster Recovery Automation

* Terraform-based Infrastructure as Code
* Recreation of VPCs, networking, compute, and database resources
* Cross-region disaster recovery support
* Infrastructure recovery automation

### Cloud Services Covered

* Amazon EC2
* Amazon VPC
* Amazon RDS / Aurora
* Amazon S3
* Route 53
* Elastic Load Balancer (ALB)
* IAM
* SNS
* CloudWatch

