## Workflow

1. Collect AWS resource inventory using AWS CLI.
2. Store infrastructure snapshots as JSON files.
3. Archive backups automatically.
4. Generate Infrastructure as Code configurations.
5. Recreate infrastructure using Terraform when required.
6. Support disaster recovery across AWS regions.

